    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_4306930692" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4306930692" />
    <a title="Bon Tom" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/40807670-bon-tom"><img alt="Bon Tom" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1511016606p2/40807670.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4306930692?book_show_action=true">Oct 26, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bon Tom" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bon Tom" href="/user/show/40807670-bon-tom">Bon Tom</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9783446244979" href="/book/show/26089109-zero-zero-zero">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/40807670-bon-tom?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4306930692" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7268283919230156979">Some call author&apos;s suggestion of legalization &quot;half hearted&quot;. Why would you, if it&apos;s obvious and only choice after reading through all the brutality and destroyed lives of whole families and communities on the one hand, and individuals that get richer than god from illegal trade on the other. Any suggestions for better solution?</span>
