              <span id="reviewTextContainer3094148802" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9581443478932749641">I got the sense that the author would have loved this to sound like it was being narrated by a character in a Tarantino film. If that is actually the case, then whatever he&apos;s tried to do here doesn&apos;t work at all. I got nearly halfway through this book, but after reading the 4 page sea-shanty listing all the various names for cocaine, my spirit was crushed. Punishing.</span>
  <span id="freeText9581443478932749641" style="display:none">I got the sense that the author would have loved this to sound like it was being narrated by a character in a Tarantino film. If that is actually the case, then whatever he's tried to do here doesn't work at all. I got nearly halfway through this book, but after reading the 4 page sea-shanty listing all the various names for cocaine, my spirit was crushed. Punishing.</span>
