        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2141696843" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17305933042119443864">If you&apos;re interested in the subject of how drugs becamse one of the rulers of the World, this is definitely the read for you. It&apos;s an immense industry in which Billions of dollars change hands. lots of lives ruined. Roberto Saviano is a brave and controversial journalist, who wrote about the fathers of the drug world and how all this system works. <br/>It was a very informative and interesting read, and at the same time very sad to learn it was so big that I could never imagine. <br/>I also listened this </span>
  <span id="freeText17305933042119443864" style="display:none">If you're interested in the subject of how drugs becamse one of the rulers of the World, this is definitely the read for you. It's an immense industry in which Billions of dollars change hands. lots of lives ruined. Roberto Saviano is a brave and controversial journalist, who wrote about the fathers of the drug world and how all this system works. <br />It was a very informative and interesting read, and at the same time very sad to learn it was so big that I could never imagine. <br />I also listened this book on Audible, and it was very good. I would definitely recommend it. </span>
