<div id="review_894853291" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/894853291" />
    <a title="Amar Pai" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/86362-amar-pai"><img alt="Amar Pai" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1363673390p2/86362.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/894853291?book_show_action=true">Mar 28, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amar Pai" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amar Pai" href="/user/show/86362-amar-pai">Amar Pai</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781594205507" href="/book/show/18114121-zerozerozero">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer894853291" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11144409439021421758">I found this to be a little verbose and rambling relative to Saviano&apos;s earlier masterpiece, <i> Gomorrah</i>. Still, Saviano deserves a lifetime achievement award for courage in reporting. So support him however you can.<br/><br/>This book is pretty current but things move so fast. Can&apos;t believe El Chapo escaped, AGAIN!<br/><br/><a href='http://www.drugpolicy.org/' rel='nofollow noopener'>stop prohibition now</a></span>
  <span id="freeText11144409439021421758" style="display:none">I found this to be a little verbose and rambling relative to Saviano's earlier masterpiece, <i> Gomorrah</i>. Still, Saviano deserves a lifetime achievement award for courage in reporting. So support him however you can.<br /><br />This book is pretty current but things move so fast. Can't believe El Chapo escaped, AGAIN!<br /><br /><a href="http://www.drugpolicy.org/" rel="nofollow noopener">stop prohibition now</a></span>
