          <a href="/book/show/1105956.Gomorrah"><img id="more_book_1105956" alt="Gomorrah" title="Gomorrah" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348324004l/1105956._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
